### 3.1 系统参数设置

```python
# TDM系统参数
fs = 8000  # 采样率 (Hz) - 电话系统标准采样率
duration = 0.1  # 信号持续时间 (s)
num_channels = 4  # 信道数量（4路语音信号）

# 时分复用参数
samples_per_slot = 200  # 每个时隙的采样点数
samples_per_frame = samples_per_slot * num_channels  # 每帧总采样点

# 时间轴
total_samples = int(fs * duration)
t = np.linspace(0, duration, total_samples, endpoint=False)

# 计算参数
frame_duration = samples_per_frame / fs  # 帧持续时间
slot_duration = samples_per_slot / fs    # 时隙持续时间
frame_rate = 1 / frame_duration          # 帧速率

print(f"采样率: {fs} Hz")
print(f"信道数量: {num_channels}")
print(f"每帧总采样点: {samples_per_frame}")
print(f"每时隙采样点: {samples_per_slot}")
print(f"帧持续时间: {frame_duration*1000:.2f} ms")
print(f"时隙持续时间: {slot_duration*1000:.2f} ms")
print(f"帧速率: {frame_rate:.1f} 帧/秒")
```

